  "enrichment": {
    "explanation": "An attacker could upload malicious objects to an S3 bucket if public ACLs are not blocked, allowing them to execute arbitrary code or steal sensitive data. To prevent this, ensure that the S3 bucket has block public ACLs enabled.",
